## Fine-tuning workflow

To adjust a motivator's behaviour during testing:

1. Open `config/motivators/oystein.ts` (or `jon.ts`)
2. Edit the `systemPrompt` text — change tone, add example phrases, adjust style
3. Save → hot-reload picks it up → test again

No need to touch any other files. The prompt text is the **only thing that controls personality**.
